{"tid":134143,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"召集所有數學高手拯救retake數科的迷途老爹","createTime":"2017-02-25T08:42:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-26T07:44:42.000Z","uid":58412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2f9f43b54bdafb4018a7ae28d498ac2a9b66e0bb","tid":134143,"uid":58412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T08:42:35.000Z","msg":"如果閣下得閒又想做下數，轉轉腦的話 <br />\n可以解答下細佬嘅難題 多謝哂 <br />\n有算式，有答案 就最好了 <br />\n<br />\n利申：數學（3）， engine科 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（1）find a formula for the inverse of the function <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/25/164107_1dd35f9edd755c9e3142f86bac07a1fc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F25%2F164107_1dd35f9edd755c9e3142f86bac07a1fc.jpg&h=7c4b6b23&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"291b1b6102c01ad93a10aafb7e5a13bbacd17089","tid":134143,"uid":41742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T08:53:12.000Z","msg":"root(x2+4.5^2)-4.5"},{"pid":"d74f343806ae668c491f1c7775343fe94c3ca880","tid":134143,"uid":34189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T08:53:14.000Z","msg":"y=sqrt(入^2+9入）<br />\ny^2=入^2+9入+(9/2)^2- (9/2)^2<br />\n自己做埋佢<br />\n<br />\n利申:wiki完 inverse function個解釋唔知有冇理解錯"},{"pid":"f3dc54aa8a05917f025563645e4e10c6ad2b74c7","tid":134143,"uid":58412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T08:57:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>root(x2+4.5^2)-4.5</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n謝巴打<br />\n<br />\n電腦顯示正確 但想問點解嘅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3953cd3107ca8283ed026e468352882183df1765","tid":134143,"uid":58412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T08:58:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>y=sqrt(入^2+9入）<br />\ny^2=入^2+9入+(9/2)^2- (9/2)^2<br />\n自己做埋佢<br />\n<br />\n利申:wiki完 inverse function個解釋唔知有冇理解錯</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nThanks ! 試緊"},{"pid":"fbd54d3ff6b9453a3bdc7f2ccbce1747a045ca49","tid":134143,"uid":58412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T09:08:53.000Z","msg":"（1）已成功解答，略略明白inverse function嘅意思 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（2）同樣地都係inverse function 但今次得兩個x 仲要加兩棟 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/30hs3o2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F30hs3o2.jpg&h=0b1835d2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8f3c6a717c9f8ae33ad4c9c95860d5528cb8d417","tid":134143,"uid":7110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T09:10:38.000Z","msg":"x&gt;0, f is surjective, inverse exists<br />\nLet y= sqrt(x^2+9x)<br />\ny^2=x^2+9x<br />\nx^2+9x-y^2=0, then sovle the quadratic equation for x."},{"pid":"bb430b451018afbbc245462a9285ac726ca1f172","tid":134143,"uid":7110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T09:13:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>（1）已成功解答，略略明白inverse function嘅意思 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（2）同樣地都係inverse function 但今次得兩個x 仲要加兩棟 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/30hs3o2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F30hs3o2.jpg&h=0b1835d2&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\nx&gt;0, f=x^2, inverse: x=sqrt (y)<br />\nx&lt;0, f=(-x)x=-x^2, inverse: x=-sqrt(-y)"},{"pid":"6b35a3123f3b32e4ea50071959b2476ec03765ff","tid":134143,"uid":58412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T09:24:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>（1）已成功解答，略略明白inverse function嘅意思 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（2）同樣地都係inverse function 但今次得兩個x 仲要加兩棟 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/30hs3o2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F30hs3o2.jpg&h=0b1835d2&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\nx&gt;0, f=x^2, inverse: x=sqrt (y)<br />\nx&lt;0, f=(-x)x=-x^2, inverse: x=-sqrt(-y)</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nThanks hku巴 電腦顯示正確<br />\n用返 x 做subject 就對了 即係<br />\nSqrt (x) and -sqrt (-x) <br />\n但下面點解sqrt出面都要(-)號嘅"},{"pid":"ea2ca735e3719c64af27a98b324fe11c30f608b7","tid":134143,"uid":58412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T09:29:25.000Z","msg":"(3) 本身做左代嗰part : (f o g), (g o f) ... <br />\n但domain 嗰度做唔到 唔明佢要咩 我只係知要interval notation only <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s1eP596.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs1eP596.jpg&h=9efab5df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/25/172923_9baf4bf2a79743325463bb1c04da9794.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F25%2F172923_9baf4bf2a79743325463bb1c04da9794.jpg&h=e635ac8e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d808274993b70ce49f42746fcddfed215c4597e8","tid":134143,"uid":58412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T09:33:49.000Z","msg":"冇高手了嗎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e4a53f70f6d13cc2e29ebf81b00814c3fa9f530","tid":134143,"uid":53186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T09:36:58.000Z","msg":"sqrt(x^2+81/4)-9/2"},{"pid":"2bb2bdce86abff62460f1d068892d340559c4d9b","tid":134143,"uid":58412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T09:38:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>sqrt(x^2+81/4)-9/2</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n(1) 已經解決左 而家做緊（3） 但多謝巴打先"},{"pid":"202d74ad2a57aecc507ad092bb11cc3a32927177","tid":134143,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T09:41:30.000Z","msg":"咁淺都要高手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c58765cde5b1dea8ac1c14484f20432228f600ba","tid":134143,"uid":58412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T09:43:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁淺都要高手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果識嘅都不妨可以解答下我嘅"},{"pid":"d00eeccb0856b514e534f04f44a36dab2c5520c1","tid":134143,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T09:58:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁淺都要高手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果識嘅都不妨可以解答下我嘅</blockquote><br />\n自己查教科書/notes啦"},{"pid":"b9ca52d1c013b7f9fdf87857e754273cb4272577","tid":134143,"uid":69125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T10:06:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>（1）已成功解答，略略明白inverse function嘅意思 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（2）同樣地都係inverse function 但今次得兩個x 仲要加兩棟 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/30hs3o2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F30hs3o2.jpg&h=0b1835d2&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\nx&gt;0, f=x^2, inverse: x=sqrt (y)<br />\nx&lt;0, f=(-x)x=-x^2, inverse: x=-sqrt(-y)</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nThanks hku巴 電腦顯示正確<br />\n用返 x 做subject 就對了 即係<br />\nSqrt (x) and -sqrt (-x) <br />\n但下面點解sqrt出面都要(-)號嘅</blockquote><br />\ny=-x^2, hence y&lt;=0 as x^2&gt;=0<br />\nso you need to take the -ve square root of (-y)"},{"pid":"36d009a8d3639eb2d8017c2040b639b052b1806f","tid":134143,"uid":41742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T10:13:06.000Z","msg":"巴打讀poly?"},{"pid":"7a5b11cd1896ec0aad1bc08f3e0aa10eda031550","tid":134143,"uid":58412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T10:20:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打讀poly?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nYes , AMA <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3873b1d75edc473c45081b65109283d177947714","tid":134143,"uid":71194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T15:07:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/obt90cqw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fobt90cqw&h=c14ce736&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n求指教x2"},{"pid":"02d81b229499ee926e614d5a0ebeb28b084071d6","tid":134143,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T15:09:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"619dc815e24be988f096f425cad8870d6061ad49","tid":134143,"uid":16613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T15:14:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>(3) 本身做左代嗰part : (f o g), (g o f) ... <br />\n但domain 嗰度做唔到 唔明佢要咩 我只係知要interval notation only <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s1eP596.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs1eP596.jpg&h=9efab5df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/25/172923_9baf4bf2a79743325463bb1c04da9794.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F25%2F172923_9baf4bf2a79743325463bb1c04da9794.jpg&h=e635ac8e&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\nDomain即係range of value of function whether it is real or not. 例如part a (f o g) 入面係21x^2-58，但係sqrt入面&lt;0就會變成unreal( sqrt of -ve no. is undefined), 所以lowest value就係sqrt(58)/21, highest value係 infinity. 下面一樣咁做"},{"pid":"28714aa555dacd1e218cc42dce667e2007bf9b75","tid":134143,"uid":16613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T15:17:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://holland.pk/obt90cqw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fobt90cqw&h=c14ce736&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n求指教x2</blockquote><br />\n兩邊開natural log做"},{"pid":"46eb9166c0107c5a78df395587ce94139b6628bf","tid":134143,"uid":65511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T15:22:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>巴打讀poly?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nYes , AMA <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nAma1110?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"438605591f2c98ead9fb1b2507c5c07125995036","tid":134143,"uid":71194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T15:23:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://holland.pk/obt90cqw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fobt90cqw&h=c14ce736&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n求指教x2</blockquote><br />\n兩邊開natural log做</blockquote><br />\n本身common log 應該點變natural log??<br />\n定係將e改做2.718282?"}]}